title: The device identifier can be copied to the clip board by clicking a
message:
The device identifier can be copied to the clip board by clicking a
button.  In the menu there is an option to send you directly to the
pushtospeech-server AppEngine website including populating the device id
to make it easy to send a message to your app.

title: A basic implementation of a GCM client that registers itself with
message:
A basic implementation of a GCM client that registers itself with
pushtospeech-server that reads the messages it receives aloud using the
TTS library.
